    "title": "Lead Instructional Designer at Mumbai University",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Mumbai University. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Instructional Designer to strengthen our Coimbatore-based team.\n\nAbout Mumbai University:\nMumbai University is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Bloom's Taxonomy\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mumbai University!",
